294
00:19:17,140 --> 00:19:21,500
Hey, you. Let go of me. Let go.

295
00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:23,550
Mom, I love you.

296
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:25,840
Stop it!

297
00:19:43,990 --> 00:19:53,800
Mi Rim, how can something so crazy like a TV drama happen to us?

298
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:57,090
If you are my aunt's niece,

299
00:19:57,090 --> 00:20:01,110
that means we're in-laws.

300
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:04,610
