305
00:20:21,310 --> 00:20:25,380
I don't know why but I feel like the bloody wind is coming our way.

306
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:27,040
Joon Oh.

307
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:34,560
Why don't we each take time to think about what to do now?

308
00:20:34,560 --> 00:20:37,390
What do you mean by that?

309
00:20:37,390 --> 00:20:39,770
What are you saying?

310
00:20:39,770 --> 00:20:45,000
I don't know. I just feel like we need to think about things.

311
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:50,760
