312
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:54,430
Seriously, what should we do now?

313
00:20:54,430 --> 00:20:56,450
I know.

314
00:20:56,450 --> 00:20:59,440
What should we do?

315
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:06,560
Ajumeoni, I don't see Jenny, Se Chan, and Se Jong.

