00:21:06,560 --> 00:21:08,610
I was going to tell you.

317
00:21:08,610 --> 00:21:13,550
The children went to see Ms. Park at her house.

318
00:21:13,590 --> 00:21:15,400
What?

319
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:17,860
Three, Six, Nine! Three, Six, Nine! Three, Six, Nine!

320
00:21:17,860 --> 00:21:19,240
- One!
- Two!

321
00:21:19,240 --> 00:21:20,260
Three....

322
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:23,260
You got that wrong.

