329
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:44,400
You worry for yourself.

330
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:46,840
Three, Six, Nine! Three, Six, Nine!

331
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:49,750
- One.
- Two!
- Three!

332
00:21:49,750 --> 00:21:51,260
Grandma, you got it wrong!

333
