335
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:02,590
Since Grandma didn't get it this time, let's call it a practice.

336
00:22:02,590 --> 00:22:03,950
Let's do it again.

337
00:22:03,950 --> 00:22:05,490
Grandma, fighting!

338
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:07,850
