339
00:22:07,850 --> 00:22:09,470
Don't worry about me.

340
00:22:09,470 --> 00:22:13,250
I was good at studying when I was in school.

341
00:22:13,250 --> 00:22:15,360
Three, Six, Nine! Three, Six, Nine!

342
00:22:15,360 --> 00:22:17,600
- One!
- Two!

343
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:20,780
- Four!
- Five!
- Six!

344
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,160
You got it wrong again, Grandma.

345
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:25,850
I can't live because of my mom.

346
00:22:25,850 --> 00:22:29,750
