347
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:32,000
- You're driving me crazy.
- Are you guys having fun?

348
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:34,250
- Have some snacks.
- I want to play too.

349
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:38,550
Okay, we will change the players now.

350
00:22:38,550 --> 00:22:41,420
Have a seat here. Three, Six, Nine! Three, Six, Nine!

351
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:43,450
- One!
- Two!
- Three!

352
00:22:43,450 --> 00:22:49,210
