353
00:22:49,210 --> 00:22:52,260
Let's just eat the cookies.

354
00:22:54,790 --> 00:22:57,060
Hyung, it was so much fun.

355
00:22:57,060 --> 00:22:58,730
Yes, it was.

356
00:22:58,730 --> 00:23:02,550
But I feel sad we can't play some more.

357
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:06,250
We can come back again.

358
00:23:06,250 --> 00:23:08,390
- Dad!
- Dad!

359
00:23:08,390 --> 00:23:11,340
- Dad.
- Yes, children.

360
00:23:11,340 --> 00:23:15,980
Did you come to pick them up? I was about to take them home.

361
00:23:15,980 --> 00:23:20,130
No, you are on your break. Of course, I should come to pick them up.

362
00:23:20,130 --> 00:23:23,270
I guess you couldn't have a rest because of the kids.

363
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:25,560
No, it wasn't like that.

364
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:29,020
Then, have a goodnight. Bye-bye, children.

365
00:23:29,020 --> 00:23:31,950
Ms. Park, how can you betray us like this?

366
00:23:31,950 --> 00:23:35,530
We promised to get some Bungeo-ppang together.

367
00:23:37,130 --> 00:23:40,650
I will buy you some, Jenny.

368
00:23:40,650 --> 00:23:45,450
Okay, it's on you, Dad. Ms. Park, let's go.

369
00:23:45,450 --> 00:23:47,230
Dad, let's go.

370
00:23:47,230 --> 00:23:48,930
Hurry, hurry.

371
00:23:48,930 --> 00:23:51,190
Let's go!

372
00:23:58,800 --> 00:24:02,310
Hyung ate the tail first.

373
00:24:02,310 --> 00:24:05,780
Noona ate the fin first.

374
00:24:05,780 --> 00:24:09,400
Where should I eat first?

375
00:24:09,400 --> 00:24:11,770
You can start with the head.

376
00:24:11,770 --> 00:24:14,930
I think it'll hurt the fish.

377
00:24:14,930 --> 00:24:17,320
I don't think I can eat this because I feel sorry.

378
00:24:17,320 --> 00:24:19,210
Give it to me then. I'll eat it for you.

379
00:24:19,210 --> 00:24:21,490
No!

380
00:24:23,010 --> 00:24:27,820
Ms. Park, why aren't you eating?

381
00:24:27,820 --> 00:24:31,820
It's because I'm full. Do you want it, Se Chan?

382
00:24:31,820 --> 00:24:34,150
Yes, I'd love to!

383
00:24:37,470 --> 00:24:41,530
Ms. Park. Did you go to the hospital?

384
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:46,580
Yes, it's okay now. Please don't worry.

385
00:24:49,830 --> 00:24:52,870
Ms. Park, please eat this.

386
00:24:52,870 --> 00:24:55,980
