387
00:24:55,980 --> 00:25:00,070
I'm okay. Please have as much as you want.

388
00:25:11,150 --> 00:25:13,810
What did you do at Ms. Park's house?

389
00:25:13,810 --> 00:25:16,590
Ms. Park made us big bibimbap.

390
00:25:16,590 --> 00:25:19,970
In a bowl this big, she mixed carrots, spinach, and eggs.

391
00:25:19,970 --> 00:25:25,890
She made bibimbap with a ton of vegetables, and it was delicious.

392
00:25:25,890 --> 00:25:26,930
Really?

393
00:25:26,930 --> 00:25:31,590
And we played the game of yut, ddakji, and the three-six-nine game!

394
00:25:31,590 --> 00:25:35,990
Dad, it's so much fun at Ms. Park's house.

395
00:25:35,990 --> 00:25:39,530
It's a hundred, thousand times more fun than our house.

396
00:25:39,530 --> 00:25:43,160
Who did you play with? With Ms. Park?

397
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:48,330
We played it with her uncle and grandma. Ms. Park couldn't play because she was sick.

398
00:25:48,330 --> 00:25:53,240
I've never seen her be like that all this time she's been with us.

399
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:56,260
I think she's really not feeling well.

400
00:25:56,260 --> 00:26:00,130
She didn't eat bibimbap nor play games with us.

401
00:26:00,130 --> 00:26:04,640
She had no energy at all.

402
00:26:04,650 --> 00:26:08,420
She seemed to be worried about something.

403
00:26:11,350 --> 00:26:14,260
What's up with you guys? Do you know about something?

404
00:26:14,260 --> 00:26:18,250
No, we don't know anything.

405
00:26:18,250 --> 00:26:21,150
It's very suspicious.

406
00:26:21,150 --> 00:26:24,950
Lee Se Jong. Won't you tell your Noona?

407
00:26:24,950 --> 00:26:30,140
Noona, please don't ask anymore. It's painful.

408
00:26:30,140 --> 00:26:34,720
What the heck are you saying? I don't want to ask as well.

409
00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:56,040
Ms. Park, you didn't look too well today.

410
00:26:56,040 --> 00:27:01,390
I will make an appointment with Dr. Kim tomorrow. Why don't you get a thorough exam?

411
00:27:01,390 --> 00:27:06,790
I feel bad since you got injured because of Se Chan and Se Jong.

412
00:27:10,020 --> 00:27:13,820
