413
00:27:13,820 --> 00:27:17,510
Thank you for your generosity.

414
00:27:20,760 --> 00:27:24,470
Are you sure you will be okay?

415
00:27:33,550 --> 00:27:36,900
[Are you sure you will be okay?]

416
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:51,610
Se Jong.

417
00:27:51,610 --> 00:27:54,600
Don't be sick.

418
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:59,010
Stay healthy and well.

419
00:27:59,010 --> 00:28:03,280
Your mom will come back...

420
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:08,510
to you for sure.

421
00:28:18,420 --> 00:28:22,310
Aigoo, aigoo. All of my body hurts.

422
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:27,520
I told you to take this regularly.

423
00:28:27,520 --> 00:28:31,880
You should have given me that earlier. You are just nagging at me without giving me a massage or so.

424
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:35,310
Here, take this. I get it!

