429
00:28:48,530 --> 00:28:52,100
But Mom, is it okay for me to do nothing?

430
00:28:52,100 --> 00:28:56,620
Don't you think I should go thank CEO Anna in person?

431
00:28:56,620 --> 00:29:01,920
