437
00:29:23,130 --> 00:29:25,520
Isn't that what a supportive partner should be doing?

438
00:29:25,520 --> 00:29:27,480
That's right.

439
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:31,000
You should go and thank her.

440
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:34,880
Tell her how much we appreciate her.

441
00:29:34,880 --> 00:29:36,890
Okay.

442
00:29:36,890 --> 00:29:39,620
Please keep drinking that.

443
00:29:39,620 --> 00:29:41,800
I drank it all.

444
00:29:45,000 --> 00:29:48,190
This is where I left it.

445
00:29:56,690 --> 00:29:58,150
My Dan Dan...

446
00:29:58,150 --> 00:30:02,280
She was so cute even as a baby.

447
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:07,480
My Dan Dan and Soo Chul...

448
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:10,350
I'll make sure to take them to the US with me,

449
00:30:10,350 --> 00:30:15,660
