463
00:31:08,450 --> 00:31:11,620
My mom's Kimchi is truly mind-blowing.

464
00:31:11,620 --> 00:31:13,370
Give it a try.

465
00:31:13,370 --> 00:31:16,820
Where's the fridge?

466
00:31:16,830 --> 00:31:19,790
It's over there!

467
00:31:21,010 --> 00:31:23,020
- You don't have to do that.
- Oh, no.

468
00:31:23,020 --> 00:31:25,300
I heard you were living alone.

469
00:31:25,300 --> 00:31:29,500
People who live alone tend not to eat very well.

470
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:34,260
You should eat proper meals from now on, okay?

471
00:31:34,260 --> 00:31:37,030
Just a moment.

472
00:31:37,030 --> 00:31:41,600
Don't mind me and take your call.

473
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:44,040
Yes, CEO Jung? Hello.

474
00:31:44,040 --> 00:31:46,320
It's Anna Kim.

475
00:31:52,670 --> 00:31:55,870
Gosh, what a nice home.

476
00:31:55,870 --> 00:31:57,970
