00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:50,550
No, please. You can go back to work.

491
00:32:50,550 --> 00:32:53,130
I'll clean this all up so that it's squeaky clean.

492
00:32:53,130 --> 00:32:55,000
No, I said it's fine.

493
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:58,080
