552
00:37:07,000 --> 00:37:10,090
No. I can't, Madam.

553
00:37:10,090 --> 00:37:12,630
I can't give up like this.

554
00:37:12,630 --> 00:37:15,840
What? If not, what are you going to do?

555
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:18,580
- What are you thinking of doing?
- When I got fired that time,

556
00:37:18,580 --> 00:37:21,280
it seemed like everything was over, but it wasn't.

557
00:37:21,280 --> 00:37:23,100
It will be the same this time too.

558
00:37:23,100 --> 00:37:25,520
So please help me.

559
00:37:25,520 --> 00:37:29,410
If you help me, I'm sure I can go back to Chairman.

560
00:37:29,410 --> 00:37:31,250
Please, Madam?

561
00:37:31,250 --> 00:37:33,630
H-help you with what again?

562
00:37:33,630 --> 00:37:35,680
I can't make Young Gook lose his memory again.

563
00:37:35,680 --> 00:37:37,650
Aigoo, Chief Jo. We shouldn't go any further.

564
00:37:37,650 --> 00:37:41,170
A person needs to know when to give up, too, when it's not working out!

565
00:37:41,170 --> 00:37:43,690
No. I can't give up.

566
00:37:43,690 --> 00:37:46,470
I can never give up!

567
00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:48,830
Oh, my...

568
00:37:52,110 --> 00:37:53,820
I can't.

569
00:37:53,820 --> 00:37:55,110
It's ridiculous.

570
00:37:55,110 --> 00:37:59,120
What is she going to do if she can't give up?

571
00:37:59,120 --> 00:38:00,910
Both Gi Ja and Chief Jo,

572
00:38:00,910 --> 00:38:02,990
I know they're mother and daughter,

