574
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:07,580
Leeches!

575
00:38:07,580 --> 00:38:09,980
The way they latch on like leeches is exactly the same too!

576
00:38:09,980 --> 00:38:12,300
Oh, gosh! I'm exhausted.

577
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:14,480
I'm so exhausted, gosh!

578
00:38:16,350 --> 00:38:19,010
Did you hear the news? The Chairman called his engagement off.

