585
00:38:42,690 --> 00:38:45,910
I thought Younger-sister-in-law was your biological mother all this time.

586
00:38:45,910 --> 00:38:49,290
Dae Beom too. I thought he was your biological brother.

587
00:38:49,290 --> 00:38:54,240
I thought you knew about everything.

588
00:38:54,240 --> 00:38:56,950
I didn't know.

589
00:38:56,950 --> 00:39:01,590
I recently found out about it by accident.

590
00:39:01,590 --> 00:39:04,960
I'm really upset.

591
00:39:04,960 --> 00:39:08,210
You're suffering away from home, working as a private tutor for someone else's household.

592
00:39:08,210 --> 00:39:12,700
Your dad is breaking his back, working to fend for his step-family.

593
00:39:18,820 --> 00:39:22,380
