594
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:24,300
But Dan Dan.

595
00:39:24,300 --> 00:39:28,020
Where did your mom go?

596
00:39:28,020 --> 00:39:31,630
Do you talk to your biological mother often?

597
00:39:31,630 --> 00:39:34,720
I wanted to ask all this to your dad,

598
00:39:34,720 --> 00:39:37,090
