00:39:37,090 --> 00:39:40,050
That's why I'm asking you.

600
00:39:40,050 --> 00:39:42,740
- My mom?
- Yes.

601
00:39:42,740 --> 00:39:46,060
Your biological mother who gave birth to you.

602
00:39:46,060 --> 00:39:48,480
Where is she living right now?

603
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:51,810
Why did she break up with your dad?

604
00:39:51,810 --> 00:39:56,500
I heard she passed away when I was young.

605
00:39:56,510 --> 00:39:58,210
What?

606
00:39:58,210 --> 00:40:01,800
Did she pass away?

607
00:40:01,800 --> 00:40:03,830
Yes...

608
00:40:03,830 --> 00:40:05,940
Oh, my goodness.

609
00:40:05,940 --> 00:40:12,550
H-How did she pass away at such a young age?

610
00:40:12,550 --> 00:40:17,300
Aunt, can you ask my dad for me?

611
00:40:17,300 --> 00:40:22,000
He won't even tell me my mom's name,

612
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:24,560
