614
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:34,840
I've been so upset all this time.

615
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:42,060
Aunt... I want to see my mom's face, at least.

616
00:40:42,060 --> 00:40:45,630
Oh, Dan Dan!

617
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,850
Wipe your tears. Don't cry, Dan Dan.

618
00:40:47,850 --> 00:40:50,040
What in the world is all this?

619
00:40:50,040 --> 00:40:54,710
