622
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:14,230
Is that why Dan Dan's mom died? Did you really do that?

623
00:41:14,230 --> 00:41:16,400
Why are you suddenly being like this, Noona?

624
00:41:16,400 --> 00:41:20,240
I'm coming back from meeting Dan Dan just now.

625
00:41:20,240 --> 00:41:21,700
Dan Dan?

626
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:24,840
No matter how much you liked Dae Beom's mom,

627
00:41:24,840 --> 00:41:27,440
how could you forget your kid, Dan Dan?

628
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:31,040
You leaving Dan Dan's mom because you had an affair with a woman who has a son,

629
00:41:31,040 --> 00:41:33,240
let's just say that's all in the past.

630
00:41:33,240 --> 00:41:37,340
But how could you not give Dan Dan a single photo of her mom?

631
00:41:37,340 --> 00:41:42,250
Dan Dan is crying her eyes out, saying she at least wants to see her mom's face.

632
00:41:42,250 --> 00:41:47,420
You can't do that to Dan Dan out of all things!

633
00:41:47,420 --> 00:41:51,070
You're wrong, Older-sister-in-law! We didn't have an affair!

634
00:41:51,070 --> 00:41:54,740
Dan Dan's mom abandoned her newborn and ran away.

635
00:41:54,740 --> 00:41:57,160
He didn't leave her!

636
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:59,810
Don't get involved in this!

637
00:42:02,300 --> 00:42:04,670
W-what are you saying?

638
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:11,060
Dan Dan thinks that Soo Chul had an affair with you, and that's why her mother died.

639
00:42:11,060 --> 00:42:14,050
You got it wrong.

640
00:42:14,050 --> 00:42:18,010
Dan Dan's mom abandoned her and Soo Chul.

641
00:42:18,010 --> 00:42:21,630
I was the one who saved Soo Chul when he was going to kill himself. Me!

642
00:42:21,630 --> 00:42:25,490
Mom, say something. You saw everything.

643
00:42:25,490 --> 00:42:27,350
Why aren't you saying anything?

644
00:42:27,350 --> 00:42:29,820
We can tell her honestly.

645
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:33,930
Why are you making me the bad person to your sister as well?

646
00:42:36,810 --> 00:42:40,020
Father...

647
00:42:40,020 --> 00:42:42,990
What's going on?

648
00:42:42,990 --> 00:42:46,040
Then...

649
00:42:46,040 --> 00:42:49,780
Then, Dan Dan's mom...

650
00:42:49,780 --> 00:42:53,290
Did she abandon our Dan Dan and Soo Chul? Is that what you're saying?

651
00:42:53,290 --> 00:42:57,410
Is that what you're saying, Younger-sister-in-law?

652
00:42:57,410 --> 00:43:00,070
Yes.

653
00:43:00,070 --> 00:43:02,510
He felt bad for Dan Dan,

654
00:43:02,510 --> 00:43:07,400
so he didn't let me say anything because she'd get hurt if she found out her mother abandoned her.

655
00:43:07,400 --> 00:43:10,910
That's why we kept it a secret until now.

656
00:43:10,910 --> 00:43:14,950
If you open up my heart,

657
00:43:14,950 --> 00:43:18,220
it's probably all rotten inside.

658
00:43:18,220 --> 00:43:22,710
Dan Dan misunderstanding me all this time was so tough and heartbreaking for me.

659
00:43:22,710 --> 00:43:27,180
But I'm going to vindicate myself now.

660
00:43:27,180 --> 00:43:32,100
It's true. Son-in-law Park and my Yeon Sil didn't have an affair.

661
00:43:32,100 --> 00:43:34,030
Absolutely not!

662
00:43:34,030 --> 00:43:38,200
Son-in-law Park asked that we wouldn't tell Dan Dan at least that

663
00:43:38,200 --> 00:43:41,800
because she'll get hurt if she finds out her mother abandoned her.

664
00:43:41,800 --> 00:43:45,870
That's why my Yeon Sil took the blame for everything!

665
00:43:48,330 --> 00:43:54,310
Then Dan Dan's mom... Where is that woman now?

666
00:43:54,310 --> 00:43:58,060
I heard she abandoned her kid and left for the US.

667
00:43:58,060 --> 00:44:03,070
We haven't heard anything from her, so we don't know if she's alive or not.

668
00:44:03,070 --> 00:44:08,440
Oh, my goodness! What in the world...

669
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:12,170
Soo Chul! Soo Chul!!

670
00:44:13,610 --> 00:44:15,610
Soo Chul!

671
00:44:24,040 --> 00:44:28,550
How can there be such a vile and evil wench like that?

672
00:44:28,550 --> 00:44:33,230
Dan Dan was crying out, saying she didn't even know her mom's face.

673
00:44:33,230 --> 00:44:36,620
I really thought my heart was going to break.

674
00:44:36,620 --> 00:44:39,470
I think Dan Dan has a lot of deep resentment.

675
00:44:39,470 --> 00:44:43,310
Why didn't you just give her some random photo and say it's her mom?

676
00:44:43,310 --> 00:44:45,930
I wanted to do that too.

677
00:44:45,930 --> 00:44:51,520
But then she would've looked at that photo every day.

678
00:44:51,520 --> 00:44:54,220
Also, if I tell her I sprayed her ashes in the Han River,

679
00:44:54,220 --> 00:44:58,420
