680
00:44:58,420 --> 00:45:02,870
How could I stand watching that?

681
00:45:02,870 --> 00:45:07,460
What do we do with our poor Dan Dan?

682
00:45:07,460 --> 00:45:14,750
How hurt would Dan Dan get if she finds out her mother abandoned her?

683
00:45:14,750 --> 00:45:19,610
It's better to think she's dead.

684
00:45:19,610 --> 00:45:26,490
Do you know how that woman's doing?

685
00:45:26,490 --> 00:45:30,130
I don't know. I don't even want to know.

686
00:45:30,130 --> 00:45:33,850
Don't talk about that woman anymore, Noona.

687
00:45:33,850 --> 00:45:37,560
Okay, I won't.

688
00:45:37,560 --> 00:45:42,920
After that day, I hated Younger-sister-in-law a lot the past few days.

