707
00:47:20,610 --> 00:47:28,890
Also, if she finds out her mom is alive, she'll go searching for that so-called mom of hers.

708
00:47:28,890 --> 00:47:32,350
I won't ever let that happen.

709
00:47:34,800 --> 00:47:37,240
Please understand me, Mother-in-law.

710
00:47:37,240 --> 00:47:42,310
I'm truly grateful that you haven't said anything until now.

711
00:47:43,860 --> 00:47:48,620
Honey. I'm so sorry to you,

712
00:47:48,620 --> 00:47:54,270
