713
00:47:54,270 --> 00:47:56,800
All right.

714
00:47:56,800 --> 00:47:59,210
I said, all right.

715
00:48:00,880 --> 00:48:07,440
I won't say anything to Dan Dan as well, Father. Don't worry.

716
00:48:07,440 --> 00:48:11,700
Okay. Thank you, Dae Beom.

717
00:48:11,700 --> 00:48:15,330
All right. I understand.

718
00:48:15,330 --> 00:48:22,940
They say, "Blood is thicker than water." For a moment, I only thought about Yeon Sil's case.

719
00:48:22,940 --> 00:48:28,380
I haven't said anything until now, so it's not hard to do the same.

720
00:48:28,380 --> 00:48:32,050
Don't worry. I won't tell her.

721
00:48:32,050 --> 00:48:34,810
Nothing happened today.

722
00:48:36,390 --> 00:48:40,990
Thank you, Mother-in-law.

723
00:48:40,990 --> 00:48:46,810
I'm sorry, Mother-in-law.

724
00:48:55,680 --> 00:48:58,350
Dan Dan?

725
00:49:02,520 --> 00:49:07,280
Her bag is not even here. Where did she go?

726
00:49:16,710 --> 00:49:21,270
The number you have called is currently unavailable. Please leave a message after the beep.

