745
00:50:52,070 --> 00:50:54,190
In this entire world,

746
00:50:54,190 --> 00:50:59,840
I'm probably the only one who doesn't know her mom's face.

747
00:50:59,840 --> 00:51:04,120
Do you know, Dad?

748
00:51:04,120 --> 00:51:10,790
When I'm sick and tired, I want to go to where my mom is buried

749
00:51:10,790 --> 00:51:16,550
